Dr. Drew Credits RFK Jr for a Large Part of His Personal Awakening: 'I Am Open to Everything Now'

"I've realized that everything in the news is BS. Everything. There is nothing I can consume on legacy media that I can trust and that is shocking...It makes you wonder how long it's been going on for...I didn't realize how much speech was being suppressed."

